Okay, this is a real AR, be careful

137
00:10:08,716 --> 00:10:16,400
But the truth is Serga and I were in another room and the players were connected and this way we discover many new insults to handle

138
00:10:19,481 --> 00:10:19,621
So

139
00:10:20,737 --> 00:10:26,179
All of this is very theoretical, so let's start with a concrete example on how it works.

140
00:10:26,739 --> 00:10:31,420
This is a playthrough from Jacksepticeye, the famous YouTuber, playing Even Zero,

141
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:34,501
and we are going to watch the first scene of the game.

142
00:10:34,521 --> 00:10:36,902
It's one minute long, and I comment it later.

143
