412
00:28:40,593 --> 00:28:44,076
You mentioned neural networks being kind of frustrating me

413
00:28:44,096 --> 00:28:46,097
because they're a black box and not easy to tweak.

414
00:28:46,177 --> 00:28:49,079
So I'm curious what you did for processing input.

415
00:28:49,119 --> 00:28:51,481
Do you guys still try to do some kind of natural language

416
00:28:51,521 --> 00:28:51,981
processing?

417
00:28:52,041 --> 00:28:54,663
Or how do you identify the user's intents, et cetera?

418
00:28:55,796 --> 00:29:01,919
So for posting inputs, we built a database based on tags,

419
00:29:01,999 --> 00:29:02,459
basically.

420
00:29:02,939 --> 00:29:07,601
Like every word with a similar meaning has a common tag.

421
00:29:07,661 --> 00:29:12,103
For example, murder, kill, et cetera, has the tag death.

422
00:29:12,864 --> 00:29:15,526
and when the player types something,

423
00:29:15,906 --> 00:29:19,049
we just check out which types are in this query.

424
00:29:19,690 --> 00:29:24,173
And the AI has answer patterns

425
00:29:24,594 --> 00:29:28,577
that are sort with the different tags

426
00:29:29,258 --> 00:29:30,239
that the player can type,

427
00:29:30,819 --> 00:29:32,381
and generate answers this way.

428
00:29:33,622 --> 00:29:34,582
Yeah.

